data.description: Make your appointment today to view this home, nestled in the beautiful subdivision of Lake Park.  One of Mesquite's most tranquil neighborhoods with tree-lined streets and wooded lots!  The exterior has great drive up appeal, a circle driveway, and a porte cochere!  This one-owner home has a nice entry, huge family, dining, and study area in a combined, open space with built-in bookcases!  The fireplace has a gas starter.  The kitchen is huge, has a built-in hutch, gas cooking and breakfast bar!  The private primary bedroom has an ensuite bath and the secondary bedrooms are oversized!  Two of the secondary bedrooms share a Jack and Jill bath.  The utility room is conveniently located off the garage along with a half bath.  Bring your ideas for updating and make this home yours!  Great access to I-20 and I-635!  Some photos are virtually staged to show possible furniture placement.
